{"tid":1633320,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有八日就過人權法 不如勇武抖幾日先！","createTime":"2019-10-07T03:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T03:45:15.000Z","uid":267311,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"073c262bc3bfcf15464d25ce2189bb1315bcc428","tid":1633320,"uid":267311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:29:00.000Z","msg":"仲幾日咋！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣上陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 煲大之前示威者受害嘅情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求大家忍下手先</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共呢幾日就係要引我地做錯！等國際無辦法支持我地！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家呢個星期斯斯文文</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉攻twitter <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去美國國會議員/官員twitter度留言share示威者受害影片相片！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6926b5b387586773051ef8264125f53241170f0","tid":1633320,"uid":267311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c5f91d5716ddfa55585690aba6d8ed184f5de2","tid":1633320,"uid":267311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8d04807c511c364a1af972c29746195cfa46cf","tid":1633320,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:29:46.000Z","msg":"長期抗爭<br />\n唔係唔出, 遲少少出都得<br />\n如果要出<br />\n裝修黨鐵同建制派, 唔好裝修商店住<br />\n香港一定要有外國人幫手制裁中共<br />\n因為我地唔係只係對住港共, 仲有史上最邪惡既政權<br />\n<span